OL,3,CMan given whole life order for
OL,4,C'bloodthirsty' murder in South London
OL,6,FA double murderer who carried out the
OL,7,F"bloodthirsty" killing of a woman and
OL,8,Fdumped her dismembered body in a park
OL,9,Fhas been jailed for the rest of his
OL,10,Flife.
OL,12,FBuilder Steve Sansom was out of prison
OL,13,Fon life licence for another murder
OL,14,Fwhen he killed Sarah Mayhew, 38, and
OL,15,Fdumped her remains in Rowdown Fields,
OL,16,FNew Addington, south London, last
OL,17,Fspring.
