OL,3,CMan given whole life order for
OL,4,C'bloodthirsty' murder in South London
OL,6,FThe 45-year-old and his partner Gemma
OL,7,FWatts, 49, have admitted murder and
OL,8,Fperverting the course of justice by
OL,9,Fdismembering Ms Mayhew's body,
OL,10,Fdistributing the parts at "various
OL,11,Flocations" and cleaning up the scene,
OL,12,Fthe Old Bailey heard.
OL,14,FIn a victim impact statement Ms Mayhew
OL,15,Fwas remembered by her mother Angela as
OL,16,Fa "beautiful, pretty girl" and she
OL,17,Fsaid "it breaks my heart she is not
OL,18,Faround".
