OL,3,CMan given whole life order for
OL,4,C'bloodthirsty' murder in South London
OL,6,FMs Mayhew's father David thanked the
OL,7,Fdefendants for pleading guilty and
OL,8,Fsaving his grieving family from the
OL,9,Fordeal of sitting through a trial of
OL,10,Fthis "horrendous case".
OL,12,FHe added: "That said whatever sentence
OL,13,Fyou may receive will never compare to
OL,14,Fthe pain you have caused us."
OL,16,F"I ask myself the same question all
OL,17,Fthe time, why did you have to kill her
OL,18,Fmaybe I will never know?"
