OL,3,CMan given whole life order for
OL,4,C'bloodthirsty' murder in South London
OL,6,FOn Thursday 30 January, Mrs Justice
OL,7,FCutts sentenced Samson to life
OL,8,Fimprisonment for murder with a whole
OL,9,Flife order which means he will never
OL,10,Fbe released from prison.
OL,12,FHe was also sentenced to five years
OL,13,Ffor perverting the course of justice
OL,14,Fto run concurrently.
OL,16,FWatts held back tears as she was
OL,17,Fsentenced to life imprisonment with a
OL,18,Fminimum term of 30 years along with
OL,19,Ffive years for perverting the course
OL,20,Fof justice to run concurrently.
