OL,4,C'bloodthirsty' murder in South London
OL,6,FIf she is ever released, she will
OL,7,Fspend the rest of her life on licence.
OL,9,FProsecutor Tom Little KC told the
OL,10,Fcourt that messages between Sansom and
OL,11,FWatts show their relationship was
OL,12,F"characterised by sado-masochistic
OL,13,Fviolence" and "such was the intensity
OL,14,Fof their relationship that they have
OL,15,Foften referred to dying together if
OL,16,Fcaught".
OL,18,FThe judge said: "Her fear and
OL,19,Fsuffering must have been acute as she
OL,20,Frealised why she was there and what
OL,21,Fwas happening.
